name: I Made My Little Brother a Cell Phone (KAP#48.0)
description: Jolynn used Legos to make her 2 year old brother, Eric, a cell phone. He promptly destroyed it... She then spent the next hour making this custom designed cell phone. Featuring a beautiful sunset background including a moon at the top, a scroll bar with home page at the bottom, and buttons for: Roblox, Youtube, Minecraft, Google, phone, and text. A cherished McCabe Family art memory from the loving and creative 7 year old. 2021. Origins: Alpha. KAP number 48.0. https://linktr.ee/kidartprojects
